data.description: Spacious and luxurious, this centrally located three bedroom townhome is what you have been waiting for. Please note that the HOA also includes gas, electrical, water, roof, yard maintenance, and grounds. The oversized Master Bedroom is spectacular with a sitting area, balcony, and ensuite bath showcasing separate his are her dressing areas that each have their own vanity, closet, and entrance. Great layout for privacy! The second bedroom is almost as spacious with a built in library wall. Down stairs you will find a large, open floor plan with plenty of room. Relax in your lovely fenced in the back garden or float under the live oaks in the refreshing community pool. Includes two reserved parking spaces. This is the largest floor plan in the complex and these units dont come on the market often.
